http://www.semanticweb.org/rgcr/ontologi.@value: Training sessions on cultural differences with all members.
Implementation of techniques for knowledge transfer among members.
Scheduling of face-to-face meetings in times reasonably compatible with all members aiming a better integration.
Analyse the hierarchy of problems, so as to determine if one problem is led by another and from that identify risks.
Perform risk management individually and analyse the impact over the hierarchy.
Evaluate each team member so a precise picture of their skills may be obtained.
Delegation of tasks according to each member's knowledge and interests, whenever possible.

Use an UML extension model.
Assign a leader for each team, who are to be responsible for the communication among all teams.
